lastmodifiedat: Mazina'igan ishkwaaj aanji' biindig $1 iw apii $2.
nospecialpagetext: Giin gagwedwe gaawiin-mashkawizi eta mazina'igan. Asab biindig mashkawizi eta mazina'igan mikan biindig [[Special:SpecialPages|{{int:specialpages}}]].
badtitletext:
Gagwedwe mazina'igan izhinikaazowin gii-maazhichige, bizhishigozi, gemaa gaawiin gwayak biiwaabiko-zagapijigan meshkwadoon-inwewin gemaa meshkwadoon-wigi izhinikaazowin.
Ganabaj biindig bezhig gemaa nawaj maajiibii'amaw gaawiin aabaji' biindig izhinikaazowin.
viewsourcetext: Giin waabam gaye naabibii'ige ondaadad biindig mazina'igan.
createacct-benefit-heading: {{SITENAME}} ayaan aanji' biindig anishinaabe indigo giin.
anoneditwarning: Ayaangwaamim: Wiin gaawiin biindigaw. Asab-asigibii'igan waabam akina anishinaabe giishpin gi ozhitoon aanji'. Giishpin gi [$1 biindigaw] gemaa [$2 ozhitoon asigibii'igewinini], gi aanji' giinawind idan gi aanji' biindig wiin aabaji'-izhinikaazowin, wiiji-nawaj bakaan debi'.
blockedtext: Gi asab'izhi-wiindan gemaa asab ganoodan biindig giba'. {{int:blockedtext-made-by|$1}} {{int:blockedtext-reason-comment|$2}} *{{int:blockedtext-start-time|$8}} *{{int:blockedtext-expiration-time|$6}} *{{int:blockedtext-intended-blockee|$7}} {{int:blockedtext-contact-blocker-admin|$1}} Gi aabajitoon "{{int:emailuser}}" gashki'o indigo bezhig anokii asab-naadazina'igane ganoodanis biindig idan biindig gi [[Special:Preferences|onaabamed]] gaye gi gaawin giba' biindig abajitoon. {{int:blockedtext-block-ip|$3}} {{int:blockedtext-block-id|$5}} {{int:blockedtext-include-details-queries}}
newarticletext: Giin maada'adoo biiwaabiko-zagapijigan biindig mazina'igan gaawiin ayaa mashi. Ozhitoon mazina'igan, maajii ozhibii'an maajiibii'amaw biindig gagwedaganaam anaamayi'ii (waabam [$1 wiiji' mazina'igan] nawaj mamizhim). Giishpin giin-bi biindig wani, ginjida' giin ningaasimoonowin azhe gibadoonh.
anontalkpagetext: ---- Wa'aw biindig idan mazina'igan biindig bezhig gaawin izhi-wiindan aabaji' awewin gawwin ozhitoon bezhig wigii-asigibii'igewinini mashi, gemaa awewin gaawin ozhitoon. Giinawind oonji' ozhitoon asigibii'igan asab-ganoodan izhi-wiindan wiinaawa. Ayaan asab-ganoodan daa nawaj maada'ookii. Indigo gi ayaan behzig gaawin izhi-wiindan ozhitoon gaye mikoojiin a'aw bagwanawizi idan ayaan idan biminizhikaw biindig gi daga [[Special:CreateAccount|Ozhitoon bezhig wigii-asigibii'igewinini]] gemaa [[Special:UserLogin|biindigaw]] biindig nawaj gaawiin wii wanim wiji nawaj gaawin ozhitooned.
noarticletext: Aazha gaawiin ozhibii'an biindig mazina'igan. Giin gashkitoon [[Special:Search/{{PAGENAME}}|nandawaabam wa'aw mazina'igan izhinikaazowin]] biindig bakaan mazina'igan, [{{fullurl:{{#Special:Log}}|page={{FULLPAGENAMEE}}}} nandawaabam inawem gikinoo'amaadii-mazina'igan], gemaa [{{fullurl:{{FULLPAGENAME}}|action=edit}} ozhitoon wa'aw mazina'igan].
noarticletext-nopermission: Aazha gaawiin ozhibii'an biindig mazina'igan. Gi [[Special:Search/{{PAGENAME}}|nandawaabam wa'aw mazina'igan izhinikaazowin]] biindig bakaan mazina'igan, gemaa [{{fullurl:{{#Special:Log}}|page={{FULLPAGENAMEE}}}} nandawaabam inawem gikinoo'amaadii-mazina'igan], aanawi gi gaawiin bagidin ozhitoon wa'aw mazina'igan.
clearyourcache: Babaamendam: Baanimaa ozhibii'igan, giin daa-ayaan izhi inose-ditibise giin ningaasimoono debibidoon izhi waabam aanji'. * Ishkode-waagosh / Bizozideshin: Dakon "Shift" ajina ginjida' Baakise-miinawaa, gemaa maagon "Ctrl-F5" gemaa "Ctrl-R" (⌘-R biibdig Mishiimin) * Gichigichi-asigibii'igan Miskwaabik-indigo: Magon "Ctrl-Shift-R" (⌘-Shift-R biindig Mishiimin) * Waasamoo-asabing Nandawaabam / Jiigewe: Dakon "Ctrl" megwaa ginjida' Baakise-miinawaa, gemaa maagon "Ctrl-F5" * Gidochige-dibaajimowin: maagon "Ctrl-F5".

Wa'aw niibiwa-mazina'igan ayaan biindig nawaj mamizhim, ondaadad biindig mazinaakizigan gemaa naabibii'ige-gashkigwaason aabaji' ozhitoon gemma atoon biindig mazinaabikiwebinigan.
Giishpin niibiwa-mazina'igan aanji' akawe ozhitoon aanind daa-gaawiin naaga' akina izhinoo' biindig niiwbiwa-mazina'igan.
